resource.title: Treatment plan for ovarian cancer
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including Surgery, Chemotherapy, Radiotherapy

resource.conclusion: Patient shows improving status for ovarian cancer. Aisha Nguyen, a 54-year-old Asian female diagnosed with Stage III ovarian cancer, underwent surgery followed by 6 cycles of chemotherapy and 15 sessions of radiotherapy. She is currently in the follow-up phase with improving status. Comorbidities include hypertension and depression. Allergic to penicillin. Social history indicates a retired teacher with Medicare insurance.
